-- INTERVIEW-Japan's Mitsui Sumitomo Insurance to lift risk assets slightly
-- By Hideyuki Sano and Takahiko Wada
-- Wed Apr 16, 2014 03:46AM EDT
-- None



TOKYO, April 16 (Reuters) - Japan's Mitsui Sumitomo Insurance Co Ltd plans to slightly increase investments in risk assets, such as foreign shares and bonds, in the financial year to March, a company executive said on Wednesday.

